# Security policy

## Reporting a vulnerability

Report security issues privately via GitHub's
[private vulnerability reporting](https://docs.github.com/en/code-security/security-advisories/guidance-on-reporting-and-writing-information-about-vulnerabilities/privately-reporting-a-security-vulnerability)
on this repository.

We aim to acknowledge receipt within 72 hours. Coordinated disclosure
windows are agreed case-by-case based on severity and downstream
impact.

## Scope

The {{ project.name }} source tree under this repository.
Vulnerabilities in third-party dependencies should be reported
upstream; this project will track and update.
